title: Introduction to C Programming
details: Learn the fundamentals of the C programming language, including syntax, data types, and basic programming concepts. Suitable for beginners.

title: Introduction to Algorithms
details: Explore the world of algorithms, algorithm analysis, and problem-solving strategies. Ideal for computer science enthusiasts.

title: Introduction to C++ for DSA
details: Master the C++ programming language and its applications in Data Structures and Algorithms (DSA). A comprehensive course.

title: Basic Data Structures
details: Deep dive into fundamental data structures such as arrays, linked lists, stacks, and queues. Essential for software developers.

title: Introduction to OOP Python
details: Learn Python-based OOP principles, encapsulation, inheritance, and polymorphism. Perfect for aspiring Python developers.

title: Software Engineering
details: Explore the software development life cycle, project management, and best practices in software engineering.

title: AWS, Cloud Computing
details: Dive into cloud computing, AWS services, and cloud infrastructure management. Gain in-demand cloud skills.

title: Database (MySQL)
details: Master the art of database design, SQL queries, and database administration using MySQL.

title: Problem-Solving Part
details: Enhance your problem-solving skills, algorithmic thinking, and programming logic. Suitable for coding enthusiasts.
